name: Rebirth.
description:
thou art sent back unto the world to live again, but the journey there shall be frought with peril. canst thou find the womb in which thou wilt be born?

designed for CEA's 48 Hour Game Jam by Alex Dault.

Thanks to Hildegard von Blingin for the use of her medieval remix of "Bad Romance", by Lady Gaga. 

Thank you to my wife Chloe for supporting me through this.
